      <title>美国码头工人和港口雇主准备重启谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-dockworkers-port-employers-set-to-restart-talks-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位熟悉谈判情况的人士透露，在罢工威胁迫在眉睫之际，美国码头工人工会领导人和代表其雇主的团体将于 1 月 7 日恢复合同谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-dockworkers-port-employers-set-to-restart-talks-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 09:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
